");'><span id='47e35eb84aff4418a359e9f01028547a_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=777&endYear=795')\">777-795年</a>，0-18岁</div><div id='47e35eb84aff4418a359e9f01028547a' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=777&endYear=777')\">777年</a>，出生。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=778&endYear=790')\">778-790年</a>，故乡家居。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=791&endYear=791')\">791年</a>，与其兄弟张复及贾餗、贾竦兄弟、白居易均住符离，且住同一里巷，时相过访。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=792&endYear=795')\">792-795年</a>，故乡家居。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"b06a58ef6cdc4d3696264f4bb92c4ddd\");'><span id='b06a58ef6cdc4d3696264f4bb92c4ddd_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=798&endYear=798')\">798年</a>，21岁</div><div id='b06a58ef6cdc4d3696264f4bb92c4ddd' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=798&endYear=798')\">798年</a>，避乱罢职。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"36a0f903943b4465b9c7356406f52058\");'><span id='36a0f903943b4465b9c7356406f52058_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=802&endYear=805')\">802-805年</a>，25-28岁</div><div id='36a0f903943b4465b9c7356406f52058' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=802&endYear=802')\">802年3月</a>，春夏间，下第东归与韩愈相别，赠诗，韩愈作《答张彻》；白居易有《邓鲂张彻落第》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=803&endYear=805')\">803-805年</a>，家居读书。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.802941,"Longitude":114.313904,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4102","Title":"开封","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"956db2efbbf94b6ea7ac8bd012422ab5\");'><span id='956db2efbbf94b6ea7ac8bd012422ab5_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=796&endYear=798')\">796-798年</a>，19-21岁</div><div id='956db2efbbf94b6ea7ac8bd012422ab5' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=796&endYear=797')\">796-797年</a>，宣武节度使从事，兼监察御史。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=798&endYear=798')\">798年</a>，宣武节度使从事，兼监察御史从韩愈学于汴州，愈妻之从女。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.210143,"Longitude":117.29235,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3203","Title":"徐州","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"c0ec1aac5ab04b5f97e764486c4f8a5e\");'><span id='c0ec1aac5ab04b5f97e764486c4f8a5e_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=798&endYear=798')\">798年</a>，21岁</div><div id='c0ec1aac5ab04b5f97e764486c4f8a5e' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=798&endYear=798')\">798年8月</a>，赴州试，为乡贡进士。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.347436,"Longitude":108.946306,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN6101","Title":"西安","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"3d2cac15bc7d4366a61b54e81fa2960a\");'><span id='3d2cac15bc7d4366a61b54e81fa2960a_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=798&endYear=802')\">798-802年</a>，21-25岁</div><div id='3d2cac15bc7d4366a61b54e81fa2960a' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=798&endYear=798')\">798年10月</a>，赴京省试。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=799&endYear=802')\">799-802年</a>，在京省试。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"ca537d2561334ddcbc680947776b0615\");'><span id='ca537d2561334ddcbc680947776b0615_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=806&endYear=813')\">806-813年</a>，29-36岁</div><div id='ca537d2561334ddcbc680947776b0615' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=806&endYear=806')\">806年</a>，赴京省试与韩愈、孟郊、张籍会合于长安，三人作《会合联句》韩愈又有《喜侯喜至赠张籍张彻》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=807&endYear=808')\">807-808年</a>，在京省试。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=809&endYear=809')\">809年2月</a>，春，进士及第复登制科，为敕头座主张弘靖以中书舍人权知贡举。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=810&endYear=810')\">810年</a>，初授京官任秘书省校书郎。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=811&endYear=813')\">811-813年</a>，秘书省校书郎。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":36.201585,"Longitude":113.123046,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN1404","Title":"长治","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"2da31d488b2d4581923fc1e990db0015\");'><span id='2da31d488b2d4581923fc1e990db0015_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=814&endYear=817')\">814-817年</a>，37-40岁</div><div id='2da31d488b2d4581923fc1e990db0015' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=814&endYear=814')\">814年</a>，昭义军节度使掌书记。李贺有《潞州张大宅病酒遇江使寄上十四兄》、《酒罢张大彻索赠诗》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=815&endYear=817')\">815-817年</a>，昭义军节度使掌书记。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.733923,"Longitude":112.796072,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN410381","Title":"偃师","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"867470b390f34e4da44b539ef82649b4\");'><span id='867470b390f34e4da44b539ef82649b4_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=818&endYear=821')\">818-821年</a>，41-44岁</div><div id='867470b390f34e4da44b539ef82649b4' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=818&endYear=819')\">818-819年</a>，任河南缑氏县主簿。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=819&endYear=819')\">819年7月</a>，七月，上尊号，朝贺礼毕，东归缑氏。张籍有《送从弟彻东归》<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=820&endYear=821')\">820-821年</a>，河南缑氏县主簿。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":39.864896,"Longitude":116.292562,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN110106","Title":"丰台","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"166ecf555cc4425b899a64d9147f1666\");'><span id='166ecf555cc4425b899a64d9147f1666_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=821&endYear=821')\">821年</a>，44岁</div><div id='166ecf555cc4425b899a64d9147f1666' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=821&endYear=821')\">821年3月</a>，幽州卢龙节度使判官、兼监察御史。张弘靖为检校司空、同平章事、兼幽州大都督府长史，充幽州卢龙节度使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=821&endYear=821')\">821年5月</a>，御史中丞牛僧儒表奏为监察御史。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=821&endYear=821')\">821年6月</a>，张弘靖密奏乞留，诏改殿中侍御史，半道还之，仍为判官。时幽州节度使张弘靖治州无方，放纵下属，激起军变，被执。张彻初至，得不杀、亦被监禁帅府。后有京中官至，张彻欲见、不得，以为军士反叛，大骂曰：“汝何敢反！前日吴元济斩东市，李师道斩军中，同恶者，父母妻子肉饱狗鼠鸱鸦。”众怒，击杀之。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=821&endYear=821')\">821年7月10日</a>，其友侯云长，请于其帅天平军节度使马总，又得张彻生前相知张恭、李元实者，使以币请之幽州，幽州人义而归之。以闻，诏所在给船輂，传归其家，赐钱物以葬。其后，韩愈有《祭张给事文》，又有《故幽州节度判官赠给事中清河张君墓志铭》<br /></div>"}],"Title":"张彻 <span class='inlineComment2'>(777-821)</span>","Detail":"<p class='inlineComment2'>引用书目：陈冠明《张彻行年稽实》　录入整理：陈冠明</p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(0, 5, 113.119328, 34.2274875, 8)\">0-25岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(0)\">宿州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(1)\">开封</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(2)\">宿州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(3)\">徐州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(4)\">西安</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(5, 10, 112.95838, 36.758465, 8)\">25-44岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(5)\">宿州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(6)\">西安</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(7)\">长治</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(8)\">偃师</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(9)\">丰台</a></p>"}]}